<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
            <h2>Welcome to Our E-commerce Website!</h2>
            <p>Thank you for joining us. Please verify your account by entering the OTP below:</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">
            <h3>Your OTP:</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">
                <%= otp%>
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">Please enter this OTP in the verification form to complete your registration.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;">
            <p>If you didn't sign up for an account, you can ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>